sub_title: Multilingual professional, solid  background in teaching foreign languages.
summary:
I am a multilingual professional with a solid track record in teaching at college and university levels and delivering excellent customer service in an international environment. I am outgoing, persuasive, team player with a strong analytical approach and focus on detail. I have a passion for working with people and constantly seek to enhance my language skills. Fluent in Dutch, German, Russian, English and Spanish.
Currently looking for a new challenge in an area where additional languages is a valuable asset.
